Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I was, and I discovered I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always right here, and it's always right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes life simple, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What else do you need to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:01:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We were on slide one of this difficult subject of reality, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people spend their whole life puzzling it, and frankly, never make much progress
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It kept me in business for 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They send them from the view to my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.06,0:01:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Paradigm's the reality, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, is this laying the way it's supposed to be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We can resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I presume we will resume.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we were on this first one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we've talked about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual evolution and reaching enlightenment, which the next major lecture will be really
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,about the inner pathway to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:02:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say, who is the I, it makes a big difference, that presumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So the unenlightened people, I is the feeler, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I is what's mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I is what's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I is what's greedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I is what's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So the I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually feeling, and this, and below 200 is all feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice there's no thinkingness there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinkingness doesn't really start until the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are whole cultures where thinkingness doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that astonishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, we presume, because we're in an intellectually arid society, let's see, what percentage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world is capable of thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the world's population, capability for thinkingness occurs in more than 10% of the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,15%.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,25%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Only 20% of the people can even think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you ask, what do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They look at you blankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I feel about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I believe about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you ask, what do you think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say to them, do you ever read the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Read the Weekly Standard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a standing joke, the Weekly Standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So they think that I'm the one that is the actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So the I is the actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And here you have the I as the volitional, the one who decides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Which of these I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:04:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So people's idea of who am I varies quite widely from the feeler to some people consider the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I as the body, I as the brain, I as the witness, I am the decider of actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The more sophisticated say, well, I'm that which experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am that which chooses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, karma would imply that the will and choice and volition are extremely important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So your feelings don't really count that much, do they, karmically?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And neither do your thoughts, because you can think anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's choosing and the volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So then karmic, up and down the karmic ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is primarily, you don't have to get on me, is primarily one of volition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the will then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The will to choose that which we consider to be aligned with God's will for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean you need to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be right, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Folks, you don't have to be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people just dread being wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the atheist decides that facing divinity at the point of death is just way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So they just quit believing in God altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, you dismiss all responsibility and accountability.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's no God, then you're not really responsible or accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So the person who dismisses God and is a devout atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I was a devout atheist for many years and also a devout agnostic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So I speak from experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But anyway, you think you sort of got rid of divine judgment and all that religious superstition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can figure, picture this atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He got rid of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He got rid of accountability.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He got rid of, you know, facing, doing a life review.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He got rid of all those worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And as he dies, he finds himself in a large chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.67,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And there he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He sees a chain with a big scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the distance, he hears,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He forgot Osiris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He negated the God of the overworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But they forgot Osiris, the God of the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And Osiris, of course, weighs your heart in the scale of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're in line with truth, you go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're not in line with truth, you go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So those of you who are still atheists, don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Osiris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If any of you are atheistic friends, you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you got rid of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's see how you're going to get rid of Osiris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So accountability is inescapable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Accountability, we have permission to ask this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is inescapable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Accountability is inescapable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So that should not strike fear into your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that's read,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,also brings in the quality of mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that another
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,quality of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is infinite mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and even if
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't make it to heaven on your own
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,if you believe in Jesus he will
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,speak for you right God will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,become you Jesus will become your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,advocate before the father right
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and in Buddhism there
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Buddha of the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,glutus land resist
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're not completely
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.42,0:08:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,on your own so there's no point to despair
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,intention then speaks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,loudly for you that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,your intention was
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to do without what you thought was
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,your capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,we were talking during the break
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,those of us that were in World War II
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,how long after
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the minute the war was over
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it didn't take even more than five seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,all of us forgave
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the people on the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't any problem
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the instant
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the war was over
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the kamikaze pilots and us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,were buddies you know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I saluted what I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,he believed in and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I admired him for it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Germans
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the valor with which they fought to the last man
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the intention was to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,serve their country
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,serve their nation serve their family
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,fulfill their
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.54,0:09:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,patriotic duty to the flag of their country
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,each one then was in a way
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,serving God in their understanding of it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so when you see that it makes forgiveness easy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you see each one of us follows our own allegiance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,now whether that allegiance is objectively true or not
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,apparently doesn't make any difference
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,God don't care
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that you follow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,your inner truth is what takes you to the next level of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,your inner truth is what takes you to the next level of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,your inner truth is what takes you to the next level of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,important
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so all these things help heal the differences in our society
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of differences and malevolence is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,contention
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact that people are different than we are they can't help being different
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,people can't help being different than
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what they are
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is that so
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,can't help but be who they are
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,hahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, does that mean everyone is innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Innocent by virtue of the limitation of the evolution of their own consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't expect a retarded person to get a straight A in biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so each one then is responsible only within the paradigm of their own reality in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, and so anyway, because this is a world of the greatest karmic opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's no point in deploring the condition of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because the world, spiritually speaking, provides the greatest of all possible karmic benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The world you see, there's no point in condemning it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,because it offers maximum karmic opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,From second to second, you're always making a decision without even realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.91,0:11:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so used to constantly making a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because options and choices are constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for human beings because they have no rest from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder they're going to sleep at night or getting drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Relief from having to constantly choose, constantly choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Every instant you're choosing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You choose this, you choose that, you choose the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.37,0:11:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And that way, like a little magnetized iron filing, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,within the infinite field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you're constantly karmically moving up or down,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,closer to heaven or closer to hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,depending on which way you're moving, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a world of maximum karmic opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So the world that I see is that this is a world of a great gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I agree, the Buddha says,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,how wondrous it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How grateful we should be to be born a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because in this world, being a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you have the option to move forward karmically.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And in other realms, you do not have such an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are the chooser, the volition and the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we tend to identify people by their social personhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, this is the virtual reality of the media,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in which for a few moments, please me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,please me, bro,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,people will do anything, strip naked in public,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,hang from the edge of a building,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,do anything to get a few moments of publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So the narcissism of the ego is extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It will go to any extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And you watch the Weather Channel or History Channel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the extremes to which men will go,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so that again,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.75,0:13:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,it gets his name and gets in them in the book
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the first man to something or other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The first man to reach something or the first man
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to get your name in the book of records.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so important to the ego, to be somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So the more you feel like you are someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the less you need the society's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And you finally reach a state where you're not interested
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in society's approval at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're indifferent to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If they approve you and like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that's very nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not necessary
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's not a goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So letting go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The social personhood then
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a superficial description,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but in today's world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,people will do anything for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,People will do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When you watch the Fox News
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes we look at it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and it just boggles our mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would a person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,would go to this extreme
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to get that one second,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that one second on the screen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I am my thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So the lower level
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,is only I am what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then as you get more evolved
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,into the 300s,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's I am what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you become very sophisticated
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and you realize that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what I am is actually
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty much a blank screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'll believe anything
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,on Monday
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and believe something else
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,on Wednesday
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that depends on how
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,we're getting programmed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,by our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The self then is either
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.27,0:15:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the content
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or it's the context.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you become
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,more sophisticated,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that which I am
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the content
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,of what I think or believe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because it changes every year
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're a year older
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am the context
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in which this scenario
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes' famous
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's very important
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to the consciousness research
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we've done
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,res interna
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,versus res external.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The world as it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of appearance,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the world as it appears
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,versus the reality
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,as it is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So discerning
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,res interna,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the world as you think it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from res external,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the reality as it is
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,requires a great deal
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,of sophistication.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And in our world,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the current academia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is ignoring this altogether
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and just saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,well, the reality is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,how I politically interpret it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.73,0:16:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,has nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,because nowadays
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,people are indoctrinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They no longer think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.90,0:16:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They no longer reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They no longer learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the purpose of education,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is indoctrination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose of education
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is no longer education
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but indoctrination
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,out of that Antioch College
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,collapsed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it's gone bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,First they applied it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to the curriculum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That brought it down
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,from 450 to 190 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they applied relativism
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to the actual functioning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of the faculty
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the running
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of the university
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the running of the university.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And it went bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not exactly a good vote
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,for Marxism.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware because we are here
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,in a university.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are in a college
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that is stunningly unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take this place
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,where we're sitting for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what academia currently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Academia, if you have permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in the U.S.,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it calibrates over 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,200, 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Academia, the great name universities,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvard, Dartmouth, Yale,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that was the backbone and strength
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that out of which the whole American economy grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellectual structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it calibrates at less than 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.83,0:18:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. The purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's formally stated,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is not to educate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but to indoctrinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. So we now have mind control.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And thought control.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So the reason we appreciate this college here today,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to calibrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This community college calibrates over 400, 430, 435, 440.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates over 440, 435.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It did calibrate 440 until we got in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So the people who went to the,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,big name Eastern Universities of the Big Ten would scoff,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, a community college.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The community colleges are the last vestige
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:19:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,of intellectual erudition and integrity in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They have all gone down,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.89,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all have sold out,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,all have collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.93,0:19:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So the fabric of the society from the intellectual viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is now non-integrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The story of the fall of anti-oncologists,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it's typical.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,William and Mary, you can name one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvard Law School is one of the most pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Harvard Law School right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvard Law School calibrates currently over 200, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvard Law School currently calibrates over 200, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvard Law School.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The law school of Harvard University,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.64,0:19:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't that shake the jello in your belly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the future of an America
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,where Harvard Law School doesn't even calibrate at 200?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the law school is now dominated by an ideology,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and unless you fulfill this ideology,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't get a license as a lawyer anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So the political power structure
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,has reached out to indoctrinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason this is so up in my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is because we are standing right here in Yavapai College,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that does calibrate at 440.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're Yale and Harvard and Princeton and University of Wisconsin.
