Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.28,0:34:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, of course, the Weekly Standard came out with the fall of Antioch College.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.11,0:34:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I began to read about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.57,0:34:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's that good book you lend me, Afagirian or Gossagirian?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.03,0:34:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gary Gossgarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.44,0:34:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gossgarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.94,0:34:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Gossgarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.36,0:34:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Gabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.17,0:34:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Gossgarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.61,0:34:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget the name of his book.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.53,0:34:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great name, Gossgarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.78,0:34:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forget that name, Gossgarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.84,0:34:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, he writes in detail about, you know, the fall of academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.73,0:34:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And at first, I didn't believe all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.65,0:34:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, this is not even possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.57,0:34:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.32,0:34:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That a professor wrote, the professors, I forget what his name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.92,0:34:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They boot him off the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.21,0:35:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the left wing says that conservatism has no rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.32,0:35:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's perfectly okay to,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.76,0:35:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, physically, uh, violently oppose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.59,0:35:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, Marcuse says, it's your duty to destroy them
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.48,0:35:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,as a person of the modern academic world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.75,0:35:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You should not allow anybody who doesn't agree with this position
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.57,0:35:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to speak in a college auditorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.46,0:35:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I am very happy that we still have enough freedom left,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.71,0:35:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is a college auditorium where I can have the freedom to say what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.84,0:35:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.07,0:35:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yavapai College.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.32,0:35:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, ha, ha, ha, ha, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.63,0:35:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.71,0:35:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Gabe, uh, tuned me in to what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.90,0:35:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I began to read about it and pay attention to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.98,0:36:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, I can't believe, uh, and I know other graduates of Eastern Universities
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.32,0:36:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,who also couldn't believe it, but they began to, uh, so, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.21,0:36:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's why we have this, send your kids to Yavapai College.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.50,0:36:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, ha, ha, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.42,0:36:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the, there's reality in, res, external.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.69,0:36:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And res Interna.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.96,0:36:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the world as it is is unknown by the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.05,0:36:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.44,0:36:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Because information is instantly processed in 1 ten thousandths of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.88,0:36:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In 1 ten thousandths of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.71,0:36:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's so hard to become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.59,0:36:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All the programs, all the feelings, all the things you have learned,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.71,0:36:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,all your belief systems, uh, your style of, uh, contextualizing,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.15,0:36:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,your style of thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.01,0:36:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding and intellectualizing etc all of this happens in 110 thousands of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.13,0:37:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,a second how can you experience what is then how can you see how can you ever
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.59,0:37:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,experience rest externa when you're stuck in rest interna the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.94,0:37:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,between them is 110 thousands of a second how can you then escape being the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.23,0:37:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,slave and the captive of the ego and that's all all its aversions and
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.86,0:37:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,attractions etc how can you get past that 110 thousands of a second well
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.75,0:37:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,people used to believe and they still do that enlightenment is the space between
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.88,0:37:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,two thoughts the Buddha taught I had some mistranslation of the Buddha but I
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.19,0:37:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,never did get to the original but the Buddha thought throughout the centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.15,0:37:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,has been that reality is glimpsed between two thoughts between two
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.19,0:37:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts you can't glimpse it between two
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.76,0:37:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.36,0:37:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because the mind works faster than 110 thousands of a second so by the time you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.92,0:38:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,notice there's a gap there you won't no longer have a gap there so it's like a
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.34,0:38:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,dog chasing its tail
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.96,0:38:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no way you can move your point of observation faster than the rate of
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.40,0:38:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,mentation of the mind itself you have to move faster than 110 thousands of a
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.30,0:38:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,second
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.01,0:38:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why practically no one ever gets enlightened one in 10,000 a second
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.96,0:38:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because you cannot move faster
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.57,0:38:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes you 110 thousands of a second
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.73,0:38:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,then to look for the space between the two thoughts and by that time the space
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.34,0:38:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is gone there's no way you can you come in light but looking for the infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.28,0:38:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,silent formless space between two thoughts not possible the Buddhas
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.09,0:38:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,alleged to have said that but he told me personally yes
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.09,0:38:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,no we've already talked about it in these previous lectures the infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.76,0:39:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,silence space is not between two thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.23,0:39:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,at age 22 it'sone channel fascinating my friends i'm not asking you to doaufultim retail ssh
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.11,0:39:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's below the thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.80,0:39:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not on the surface of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.17,0:39:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like one wave chasing another
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.28,0:39:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're gonna find a place between the waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.21,0:39:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the silence and the stillness is below the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.90,0:39:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've spoken of this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.88,0:39:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So as a style of contemplation,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.98,0:39:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,what you do is you disconnect from the particularity,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.63,0:39:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the linearity of the worldly phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.57,0:39:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and you become awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.30,0:39:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You become the field of awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.21,0:39:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you move from participant, experiencer,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.88,0:39:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,back to witness, to observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.80,0:39:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you get that the only reason
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.88,0:39:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you're able to witness or observe
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.61,0:39:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is because there is a infinite formless field
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.51,0:39:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and you move back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.28,0:39:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of I moves from out there
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.69,0:40:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,or what people think of you out there
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.48,0:40:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,or what's said out there
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.61,0:40:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,or what you believe out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.73,0:40:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It moves and you realize the one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.48,0:40:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that doesn't change is the witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.88,0:40:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always the same witnesser.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.32,0:40:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, you can be a Democrat one year
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.17,0:40:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and 10 years later be a Republican,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.38,0:40:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but the witnesser doesn't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.82,0:40:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So I am that which, I am the witnesser.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.57,0:40:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the witnesser of the phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.21,0:40:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,as they go through the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.48,0:40:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you become even more sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.86,0:40:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You realize that you are prior to witnessing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.82,0:40:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,because witnessing can happen
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.98,0:40:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own, but how does one know
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.46,0:40:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that witnessing is even happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.25,0:40:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,There is therefore something more a priori,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.21,0:40:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,more fundamental to the witness
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.17,0:40:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.28,0:40:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So the sense of self moves from the individual ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.13,0:40:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the narcissistic ego, all about me and I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.48,0:41:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and my tube and YouTube and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.53,0:41:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, and I'm beginning to say that's boring BS.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.86,0:41:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's really a lot of BS out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.59,0:41:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And it withdraws its interest from that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.53,0:41:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it says, how do I know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.67,0:41:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it says, well, who is the I?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.36,0:41:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who is the I that believes things?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.80,0:41:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The I believed this then and it believes this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.50,0:41:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a different I?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.90,0:41:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So you begin to find something that is always present.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.59,0:41:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What is always present?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.92,0:41:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will finally end up as you're in deep meditation,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.61,0:41:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go of all of attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.19,0:41:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let go of attachments and aversions,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.34,0:41:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,if you let go of attachments and aversions,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.51,0:41:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and all thinkingness, yes, and all ideation
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.55,0:41:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and all symbolism and all the stuff that goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.05,0:41:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in the mind, you end up with awareness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.61,0:42:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That that which I am is no different than awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.05,0:42:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But that in itself then becomes a belief system, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.96,0:42:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, when let's go, even the thinking or the belief
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.07,0:42:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of self as experiencer, as the consciousness out of which
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.26,0:42:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,your experiencing arises, and the identity between the self
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.71,0:42:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is the substrate of the self,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.46,0:42:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,then suddenly disappears, suddenly disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.82,0:42:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And as it disappears, you feel yourself die.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.78,0:42:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So people write me periodically, they feel they're dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.65,0:42:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, good, wonderful, because that which you really are
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.09,0:42:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot die, so what you're experiencing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.36,0:42:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is the death of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.07,0:43:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens then is the mind becomes progressively silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.55,0:43:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you're in nonlinear realms, nonlinear realms,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.28,0:43:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,not within mind itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.34,0:43:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in realms of much greater dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.15,0:43:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the realms of context, not of content.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.03,0:43:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And so in the beginning, you think of self in terms
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.26,0:43:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of content, I am me, I'm 62 years old, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.11,0:43:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then finally, you begin to experience self as context.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.82,0:43:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the context out of which arises awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.88,0:43:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,believingness, witnessing, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.57,0:43:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And you begin to move farther and farther back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.82,0:43:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you will come to what I would call,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.30,0:43:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially, it was like a high, pristine place.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.84,0:43:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like being in the top of the highest mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.32,0:44:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the highest Andes, completely, altitude is the closest analogy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.98,0:44:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Infinite silence, nothingness, there's nothing there, no thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.78,0:44:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no one to experience anything there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.69,0:44:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And you go through the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.19,0:44:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The void is at calibration level 850.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.76,0:44:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the level confronting.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.03,0:44:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This entity, at age three, came out of oblivion
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.05,0:44:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,into nothingness and confronted with,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.61,0:44:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,is the ultimate reality allness or nothingness?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.01,0:44:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And that took decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.76,0:44:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, when you feel like you're dying, that's terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.34,0:44:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When you feel like you're dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.78,0:44:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,when your whole mind is silenced, it disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.90,0:45:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,When you feel yourself die, because you feel yourself die.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.61,0:45:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a belief system.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.84,0:45:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are dissolves and you feel the self die.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.46,0:45:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will tell you, it is, for a few moments, in extreme agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.55,0:45:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All that you ever thought you were, believed you were,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.71,0:45:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced yourself were, through all the lifetimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.76,0:45:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,zillions of lifetimes, you're letting it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.13,0:45:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you realize, to reach enlightenment, this too, O Lord, I must give up to thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.13,0:45:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You give up everything, one thing after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.44,0:45:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Desires and wishes and aversions and thoughts and belief systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.61,0:45:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,politics, religion, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.57,0:45:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You give it all up to find the ultimate reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.78,0:45:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The last thing you're holding back is life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.42,0:46:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then came the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.36,0:46:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I realized that this too, O Lord, must I lay down to thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.53,0:46:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, there is a moment of agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.17,0:46:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Of agony, in which you feel yourself actually die, and you do die.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.65,0:46:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that which you think is you, is what's dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.42,0:46:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it was the real you, you know, nothing would be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.67,0:46:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The real you dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.11,0:46:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taking the big jump that's leaping off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.51,0:46:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, to thee, O Lord, I surrender my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.98,0:46:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And then came the agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.53,0:46:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the agony stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.65,0:46:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then ecstasy beyond all description.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.09,0:46:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And the world was reborn and radiated forth the divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.03,0:47:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and the incredible beauty of all that exists throughout all of time
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.11,0:47:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in the reality of your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.86,0:47:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And you run, that is what's called Unio Mystico, the God within,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.44,0:47:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,God immanent, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.86,0:47:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then life is totally transformed, experientially and in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.40,0:47:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what it's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.40,0:47:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.23,0:47:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it's all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.28,0:47:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's meaning, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.82,0:47:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that is the ultimate reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.19,0:47:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That there is no reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.65,0:47:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no reality to become, to refuse, to ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.73,0:47:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is and that which you are are one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.65,0:47:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And the thing that marks it as the ultimate reality is its stunning beauty, but its stunning
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.05,0:48:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the most staggering thing about
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.73,0:48:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,after going through this high pass
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.90,0:48:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of absolute voidness
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.30,0:48:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden the earth shone forth
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.05,0:48:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,with incredible beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.36,0:48:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind is silent
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.67,0:48:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,in the witnessing of the incredible beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.84,0:48:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.78,0:48:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,essence of all things shine forth
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.00,0:48:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.40,0:48:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,God as the essence of all that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.84,0:48:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,exists shines forth so all
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.80,0:48:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you see is divinity wherever you look
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.86,0:48:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,which pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.15,0:48:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,takes you out of operating in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.00,0:48:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for quite a while
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.07,0:48:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,actually
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.46,0:48:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,then if karmically
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.80,0:48:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,karmically
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.69,0:48:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,predestined
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.61,0:48:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or not predestined but destined
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.90,0:48:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,as a capacity one might return
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.65,0:48:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to the world and speak
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.55,0:48:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of such matters but it's totally unnecessary
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.82,0:48:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.13,0:48:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,hardly needs you to validate that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.26,0:49:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is is the ultimate
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.23,0:49:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hardly needful
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.88,0:49:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of you to
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.46,0:49:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,attest to it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.80,0:49:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,however
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.46,0:49:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in a group like this
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.57,0:49:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we have many strange people
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.61,0:49:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,who wish to reach enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.32,0:49:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,oh boy
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.76,0:49:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what an exciting and wonderful journey
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.15,0:49:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it is how exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.55,0:49:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and wonderful it is
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.86,0:49:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you move one paradigm of reality onto
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.53,0:49:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,a broader one
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.46,0:49:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you move from content to context
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.00,0:49:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you end up with
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.53,0:49:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,isness and beingness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.23,0:49:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then if you've got a good
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.11,0:49:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,conscience
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.11,0:49:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you go to a越 place
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.11,0:49:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a good feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.11,0:49:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,then it will be
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.34,0:49:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,a learning
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.34,0:49:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,it will be
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.34,0:49:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,a state of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.34,0:49:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the state of space
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.34,0:49:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.34,0:49:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for example
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.34,0:49:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,a teacher would warn you about the void
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.34,0:49:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you make it through the void
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.34,0:49:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and i've told you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.34,0:49:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,when you get to the void
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.34,0:49:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to refuse it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.34,0:49:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the void of nothingness
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.53,0:49:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is devoid of god's love
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.53,0:50:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and you reaffirm
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.53,0:50:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.53,0:50:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.53,0:50:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is infinite love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.53,0:50:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is void
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.53,0:50:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is fallacious
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.36,0:50:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,so you breach that gap
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.36,0:50:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,at consciousness level 850
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.36,0:50:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the ultimate is not nothingness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.42,0:50:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the ultimate is allness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.86,0:50:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and the allness of divinity is nothingness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.13,0:50:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.88,0:50:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is powerfully love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.86,0:50:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so whatever state you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.40,0:50:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,arrive in if it isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.11,0:50:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,overwhelmingly love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.75,0:50:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then refuse it and go on
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.17,0:50:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what it is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.63,0:50:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because the infinite love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.69,0:50:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is the unmistakable sign
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.42,0:50:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,there is first of all
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.32,0:50:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,motionless incredible beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.15,0:50:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you see everything unfolding
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.19,0:50:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,as its essence
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.88,0:50:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,presents itself
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.84,0:50:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you witness the essence of everything
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.44,0:50:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.65,0:50:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,essence you become aware
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.69,0:50:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of its divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.69,0:50:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and as an essence of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.42,0:50:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,is infinite love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.92,0:50:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so I say dogs and cats are divine
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.82,0:51:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,if I look at the kitty
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.67,0:51:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say hi kitty
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.44,0:51:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the kitty goes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.42,0:51:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.82,0:51:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that the most miraculous thing in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.90,0:51:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,she doesn't even speak English
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.51,0:51:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,if I say
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.23,0:51:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bowser
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.46,0:51:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Bowser
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.21,0:51:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the radiation of love shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.69,0:51:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the divinity shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.40,0:51:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,through the dog and the cat
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.76,0:51:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so maybe the first place you can find it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.78,0:51:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard to find in your fellow man
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.42,0:51:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you had a really good mom
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.59,0:51:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes good cakes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.01,0:51:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you got a good wife
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.51,0:51:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so the source of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.46,0:51:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.19,0:51:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is within you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.26,0:51:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,it radiates forth into the world
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.38,0:51:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,as loving
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.07,0:51:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the quickest pathway to God
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.05,0:51:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.98,0:52:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,choose the lovingness
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.50,0:52:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of your existence
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.63,0:52:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and share that lovingness with others
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.48,0:52:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.13,0:52:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,between life and death
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.50,0:52:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,people reach the end of their rope
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.84,0:52:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and you smile at them
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.59,0:52:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and say hi
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.50,0:52:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly they decide to live
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.69,0:52:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.30,0:52:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so the good actions that you perform
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.69,0:52:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,build up something
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.21,0:52:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that I never read about
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.42,0:52:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I never hear about
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.07,0:52:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is you build up a karmic bank
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.50,0:52:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,a bank account
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.38,0:52:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a positive balance
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.67,0:52:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in your karmic bank account
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.07,0:52:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can remember drawing on that positive bank account
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.96,0:52:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you know all the good deeds
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.26,0:52:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you think well I did all those good deeds
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.61,0:52:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't get any reward
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.57,0:52:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,no but boy have you ever got a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.63,0:52:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's growing at 10% in a year
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.86,0:52:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,one time I'm driving my old truck
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.03,0:52:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which I still have
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.51,0:52:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and it broke down
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.86,0:53:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a million miles from anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.78,0:53:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody knew I was even there
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.98,0:53:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't have the strength
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.46,0:53:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to take the big tire off
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.32,0:53:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get the crank to work
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.75,0:53:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and I didn't have the strength
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.44,0:53:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to jack it up anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.46,0:53:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so I stood there forlorn
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.80,0:53:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.40,0:53:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in this very remote place
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.88,0:53:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.07,0:53:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,drives up a car
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.36,0:53:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,pulls up to me and says
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.96,0:53:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,hi Dave you're stuck I'll help you out
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.13,0:53:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,things like that have happened to me
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.15,0:53:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.00,0:53:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.34,0:53:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and people say
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.00,0:53:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,oh yeah that's just an accident
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.59,0:53:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,no it's not an accident
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.71,0:53:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's like you had a positive
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.65,0:53:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,bank karmic bank account
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.42,0:53:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you need it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.82,0:53:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,wow somebody pulls over
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.17,0:53:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the same thing happen
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.40,0:53:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in a complicated one of those things
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.76,0:53:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,going into Sedona
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.88,0:53:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean going into Phoenix
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.26,0:53:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to get to the airport
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.61,0:53:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the old truck broke down
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.03,0:53:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,on this whatchamacallit
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.88,0:53:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and this old truck pulls over
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.92,0:53:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,he says what you're broken down
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.15,0:54:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I can't get this wheel off
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.03,0:54:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's flat
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.78,0:54:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he says I'll help you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.90,0:54:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,he got out
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.57,0:54:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,he took it off
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.21,0:54:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,he threw it in his truck
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.30,0:54:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,he went down
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.98,0:54:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,got off the next exit
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.40,0:54:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,went to his garage
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.78,0:54:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,got it fixed
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.44,0:54:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,came around back up
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.55,0:54:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,through the court of relief
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.26,0:54:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,came back and pulled up next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.03,0:54:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and says here I'll put it on for you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.59,0:54:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,he took it off
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.57,0:54:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,he went and got it fixed
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.73,0:54:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,put it back on for me
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.36,0:54:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,all right
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.63,0:54:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll just ask one last question
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.86,0:54:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,then we'll break for lunch
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.61,0:54:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.21,0:54:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that man was an angel
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.01,0:54:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,resist
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.94,0:54:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so there are angels
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.92,0:54:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.65,0:54:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean what but an angel
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.09,0:54:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,would sacrifice hours of their time
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.44,0:54:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,go out of their way
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.34,0:54:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,loop around
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.11,0:54:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,loop back again
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.98,0:54:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and we bring angels into our experience
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.76,0:54:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because of our own reservoir
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.80,0:54:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of positive karma
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.88,0:55:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't that a nice thing to know
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.59,0:55:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,if that don't warm your heart up
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.38,0:55:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,for lunch time
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.19,0:55:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what will
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.15,0:55:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll see you again at what time
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.61,0:55:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,see you again at two o'clock
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.53,0:55:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.80,0:55:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.92,0:55:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,oh it's hard to take it all seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.65,0:55:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I say
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.40,0:55:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,never take it seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.19,0:55:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but look like you do
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.19,0:55:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so people don't get offended
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.63,0:56:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you're telling you all about
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.76,0:56:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,their gallbladder operation
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.98,0:56:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you think oh my god
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.23,0:56:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.51,0:56:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and then what
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.19,0:56:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.55,0:56:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,oh right here right now
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.71,0:56:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,same place every time
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.63,0:56:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, certain things we emphasize that I've said before.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.53,0:56:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I said there's two kinds of learning, left brain linear, sort of memorization, intellectual, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.34,0:56:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's sort of a right brain holistic knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.40,0:56:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the whole bundle, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.13,0:56:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain things I emphasize because they're rarely said.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.98,0:56:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're rarely said from a certain energy level.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.80,0:56:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I say them because you may not need them in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.90,0:56:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But in some lifetime, those of you who have chosen enlightenment as a direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.23,0:57:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,then have chosen your own evolutionary path.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.03,0:57:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you choose enlightenment as an evolutionary path, the end is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.05,0:57:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.00,0:57:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,One who sticks to the evolutionary path to enlightenment becomes enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.84,0:57:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.19,0:57:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.09,0:57:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.71,0:57:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it behooves me to tell you things I know you can't get elsewhere that you need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.01,0:57:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, it's your intellect that's heard it before, but I'm not speaking to your intellect now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.96,0:57:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm speaking to the auric energy, the energy of your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.63,0:57:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.21,0:57:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the information is that having abandoned everything, the pathway of negation, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.59,0:57:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not this, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.51,0:58:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither attractions nor aversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.32,0:58:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You go into further and further rarefied places in which there's nothing left really to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.44,0:58:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I said, the only thing you've got left to surrender is life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.23,0:58:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You've let go of all attractions and aversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.71,0:58:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Money, fame, the opposite sex, women, children, architecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.57,0:58:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You even let go of beauty, possessions.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.76,0:58:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.36,0:58:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.15,0:58:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If it hangs in, it hangs in.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.30,0:58:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If it doesn't, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.25,0:58:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.42,0:58:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't mean anything one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.65,0:58:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't care if it's there or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.07,0:58:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, most people care about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.38,0:58:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's a certain level where you don't care whether it goes on or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.30,0:58:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a modest curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.23,0:59:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice if it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.55,0:59:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it doesn't, it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.09,0:59:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.36,0:59:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually arrive at a situation like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.67,0:59:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And you end up in a really advanced state, as I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.13,0:59:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a rarefied stratosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.98,0:59:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's nothing to let go of.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.71,0:59:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.61,0:59:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.28,0:59:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing left to let go of.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.88,0:59:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go of every attraction, every aversion, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.94,0:59:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, at least in this experience, it's on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.01,0:59:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That the one thing you are clinging to is life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.28,0:59:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're clinging to is life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.48,0:59:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the experience of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.21,0:59:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.67,0:59:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the acquisitions or the aversions of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.46,0:59:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But that core that gives you a sense of reality is life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.86,0:59:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it dawns on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.84,1:00:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This too, O Lord, must be surrendered to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.42,1:00:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To thee, O Lord, I surrender my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.13,1:00:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then comes up the terror.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.40,1:00:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.21,1:00:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment of the terror, there has to be already within your aura.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.46,1:00:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The absolute knowingness of somebody who has absolutely transcended this level.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.69,1:00:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That it's absolutely safe and to surrender all fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.05,1:00:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There comes forth a knowingness spontaneously, autonomously.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.98,1:00:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not out of thinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.73,1:00:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But out of a knowingness that all fear is illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.90,1:00:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear of the loss of life is just another illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.21,1:00:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But the last one.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.90,1:00:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you proceed to let go of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.44,1:00:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Life.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.51,1:00:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Life.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.67,1:00:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, at that point, the terror comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.80,1:00:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And at that point, you need a conviction from the absolute.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.80,1:01:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The absolute can only be conveyed by somebody who has actually lived through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.92,1:01:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the value of the spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.53,1:01:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The transmission of the energy fuel through the aura which you've read about.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.28,1:01:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And which happens here and now as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.76,1:01:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The absolute knowing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.78,1:01:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The reliance on it must be absolute.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.86,1:01:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.48,1:01:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're letting go of absolutely all that you think you are and believe that you are since the beginning of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.92,1:01:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That which has gone through that path, passage, with the absolute knowingness that you can do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.88,1:01:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the energy of that knowingness is now in your aura.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.75,1:01:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Having, you've heard it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.84,1:01:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not remember it for 5,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.17,1:02:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.53,1:02:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In this instance, it came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.98,1:02:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't the product of a stream of thinkingness or reason or logic or memory.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.57,1:02:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.84,1:02:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.50,1:02:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.92,1:02:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of nowhere came the knowingness resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.32,1:02:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The knowingness came as a radiation from the aura of the teacher resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.05,1:02:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher from which I picked it up was over a thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.32,1:02:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,2,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.21,1:02:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,2,500.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.92,1:02:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 2,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.69,1:02:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher from whom I picked it up was over 2,000 years ago, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.48,1:02:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not thinking about what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.00,1:02:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It was over 1,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.61,1:02:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,1,500 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.84,1:02:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,1,200 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.28,1:02:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,1,300 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.55,1:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to ask permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.07,1:02:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.84,1:02:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.05,1:03:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.25,1:03:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because I'm just trying to convey a knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.90,1:03:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the knowingness is now theirs.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.09,1:03:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to know at a certain point that it's safe to put your foot there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.80,1:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if it's the wrong place, you're going to drown.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.03,1:03:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's safe to put your foot there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.92,1:03:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe to let go then of that tether to life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.94,1:03:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.48,1:03:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done my duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.88,1:03:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said it.
