Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.00,1:11:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we see is that little minority that did learn how to maneuver in the linear domain.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.75,1:11:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And science, of course, is our biggest gift.
